(1) Body of female; (2) Body of male; (3) Tergites VII-X of male; (4) Meso and metanotum; (5) Head and pronotum; (6) Sternites III-VII of female; (7) Tergites VIII-X of female; (8) Forewing of male; (9) Antenna.
